      <title>git</title>
      <link href="/2022/04/14/git/"/>
      <url>/2022/04/14/git/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Git环境配置"><a href="#Git环境配置" class="headerlink" title="Git环境配置"></a>Git环境配置</h2><p>​<strong>查看git用户名</strong> <code>git config user.name</code></p><p>​<strong>查看git密码</strong>  <code>git congfig user.password</code></p><p>​<strong>配置git用户名</strong>  <code>git config --global user.name &quot;新的用户名&quot;</code></p><p>​<strong>配置git邮箱</strong>  <code>git config --global user.email &quot;新的邮箱&quot;</code></p><p>​<strong>查看系统配置</strong>  <code>git config --system --list</code></p><p>​<strong>查看用户配置</strong> <code>git config --global --lsit</code></p><h2 id="Git常用命令"><a href="#Git常用命令" class="headerlink" title="Git常用命令"></a>Git常用命令</h2><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">remote directory</span><br><span class="line"> git push        git pull</span><br><span class="line">     history</span><br><span class="line"> git commit      git reset</span><br><span class="line">     stage</span><br><span class="line"> git add files   git chectout</span><br><span class="line">     working directory</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git status [filename] : 查看指定文件状态</span><br><span class="line">git status : 查看所有文件状态</span><br><span class="line">git add . 添加所有文件到暂存区</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m ：提交暂存区的文件到本地仓库</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Git配置SSH公钥"><a href="#Git配置SSH公钥" class="headerlink" title="Git配置SSH公钥"></a>Git配置SSH公钥</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> C:\Users\user\.ssh</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa <span class="comment">#生成密钥</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>将生成的id_rsa.pub文件里的内容复制到码云中</strong></p><p><img src="/pic/git/p1.png" alt="1649930110699"></p><h2 id="创建Git项目"><a href="#创建Git项目" class="headerlink" title="创建Git项目"></a>创建Git项目</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> 文件夹 </span><br><span class="line">git init</span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> url</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="DOS-和Shell-区别"><a href="#DOS-和Shell-区别" class="headerlink" title="DOS 和Shell 区别"></a>DOS 和Shell 区别</h2><table><thead><tr><th>功能</th><th>cmd</th><th>linux</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>列举文件</td><td>cls</td><td>clear</td></tr><tr><td>创建目录</td><td>mkdir</td><td>mkdir</td></tr><tr><td>删除目录</td><td>rd</td><td>rmdir</td></tr><tr><td>在屏幕打印文件内容</td><td>type</td><td>cat</td></tr><tr><td>删除文件</td><td>del</td><td>rm</td></tr><tr><td>移动文件</td><td>move</td><td>mv</td></tr><tr><td>清除屏幕</td><td>cls</td><td>clear</td></tr><tr><td>列举文件</td><td>dir</td><td>ls</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
